high_descs: Walk to the stove, turn right and walk to the end of the counter on the right, turn left and walk to the counter.
Pick up the apple between the microwave the the green sponge.
Turn right, walk to the wall, turn left and face the microwave.
Open the microwave door, place the apple on the plate inside, close the door and turn the microwave on.  When the microwave turns off, open the door, remove the apple, and close the microwave door.
Turn left, walk toward the stove, turn right and face the counter.
Place the apple on the counter in front of the head of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Heat up the apple in the microwave and place it on the counter by the lettuce.

high_descs: Walk straight, turn right near the stove, walk straight and turn left when you see a sponge on the counter top.
Pick up the yellow apple near the microwave on the counter top
Go to the right a little bit to go to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the apple in it, close the microwave, let it heat for a while, pick it up again and close the microwave.
Go to the left and turn right before the toaster on the counter top.
Put the apple in front of the lettuce on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple in front of the lettuce on the counter top.

high_descs: Walk ahead and veer right to the microwave.
Pick up the apple on the left side of the microwave.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Take a few steps left to the part of the counter with the toaster on it.
Place the apple on the counter in front of the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple on a counter.
